{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow self-builders to use their LISA for building costs not just land purchase",
        "additional_details": "Allowing self-builders use their LISA for building costs might help people financing their self-builds, which would be helpful in the housing crisis, especially in places with lower land prices. \r\n\r\nA LISA can be used for both the building and land when buying an already built house, so it should be the same for self-builds too.\r\n",
        "background": "Right now self-builders can use their Lifetime ISA (LISA) for land purchase if they have a mortgage. We believe this punishes those who can buy a cheaper land outright, but still need a mortgage for the build itself.",
